<br>
Robe of the Elements requires to to kill 20+ level mobs for NODROP items in SolA, Permafrost and Lesser Faydark (fire goblin skin, frost goblin skin, twice woven cloak).  You could probably do it with a group mid-20s.  I did it solo at 29.<br>
<br>
The frost goblin skin is neat to get because it looks like leather.  Not that mages need to disguise themselves. <p>--------------------------<BR>
Kennethjames Scrubfire<BR>
Mage of the 46th 
Summoning, Mithaniel Marr<BR>
Member of the guild Dragon Maw<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=felwar>Felwar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(7/4/01 3:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerequipmentandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=731.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Levels for Quest Items and Robe of the Elements</span><hr size=1> Alligators in Cazic Thule will drop the shovel, stien, etc.  They are about low twenties,<br>
but you will want to group hunt them due to the nature of the zone (at 29 I was unable<br>
to solo them effectively).<br>
If you are lower level get the items from the magicians in Najena... they range from mid<br>
to high teens and I was able to solo them no problem at 23-24.  Grouping you should<br>
be able to take them out at a much younger age.<br>
<br>
<br>
